title: Wonder Man - (Danny Kaye 1945).avi
description:

Full screen, color, quality is good enough to be a dvdrip but I&#039;m not sure that it was.  It may be a high quality VHS. It shows up very good on 22 inch wide screen monitor.  English only, no subs.


IMDB:
Boisterous nightclub entertainer Buzzy Bellew was the witness to a murder committed by gangster Ten Grand Jackson. One night, two of Jackson&#039;s thugs kill Buzzy and dump his body in the lake at Prospect Park in Brooklyn. Buzzy comes back as a ghost and summons his bookworm twin, Edwin Dingle, to Prospect Park so that he can help the police nail Jackson.
